{"_id":"qmWpZe66DvEDeYIS","name":"Marchand","type":"metier","img":"icons/svg/hanging-sign.svg","system":{"description":"<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>INT minimum :</strong> 12, <strong>CHA minimum :</strong> 11</span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Restrictions :</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">➢</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">n&rsquo;utilise pas d&rsquo;armure sup&eacute;rieure &agrave; PR3 (sauf magique)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">➢</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">ne peut utiliser d'arme &agrave; 2 mains</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>EV initiale : </strong>selon origine</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">En raison de son &eacute;rudition, au niveau 1 le marchand doit retirer 1 point &agrave; l'attaque ou &agrave; la parade, qu'il pourra ajouter au&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">choix &agrave; l'intelligence ou au charisme.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Au niveau 1, le marchand poss&egrave;de une charrette, un cheval et une &laquo; maison en village paum&eacute; &raquo; (&agrave; situer sur la carte)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Comp&eacute;tences h&eacute;rit&eacute;es :</strong> </span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.BanlooIvmEVtM04V]{APPEL DES RENFORTS}</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.ic0rqdy7Mthlc3WM]{ARNAQUE ET CARAMBOUILLE}</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.jNIsR4eKWVvtYJwo]{&Eacute;RUDITION}</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.GhZr8UzASIu08NN6]{FARIBOLES}</span></span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.4xN6eJigOPkkFYfT]{M&Eacute;FIANCE}</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Comp&eacute;tences au choix : </strong></span></span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.7hsO8i9phM8psCqO]{CHEF DE GROUPE}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.2FdTwRRaWK5kZCpm]{CHEVAUCHER}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.nd64d5ja4nDklC0r]{CUISTOT}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.SjOFeBgQ76iaBayl]{FORGERON}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.aKTdj8Vd1JYWkQDW]{INST