{"_id":"sbfRuZ3iPZ1XC4Ow","name":"Ninja, Assassin","type":"metier","img":"icons/svg/hanging-sign.svg","system":{"description":"<p><strong>AD minimum : </strong>13</p>\n<p><strong>Restriction :</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">➢</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"> </span>n&rsquo;utilise pas d&rsquo;armure sup&eacute;rieure &agrave; PR3 (sauf magique)</p>\n<p><strong>EV initiale : </strong>selon origine</p>\n<p><strong>Valeur ATTAQUE initiale :</strong> 11 (bonus AD compris) &ndash; Valeur PARADE initiale : 8</p>\n<p>L'assassin est bien meilleur &agrave; l'attaque qu'&agrave; la parade. De plus, apr&egrave;s avoir r&eacute;ussi une esquive, il a 50 % de chances de&nbsp;pouvoir attaquer tout de m&ecirc;me au cours de l'assaut suivant (4, 5 ou 6 au D6).</p>\n<p><strong>Comp&eacute;tences h&eacute;rit&eacute;es :</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.MhLhVi8bOo2M3yFU]{D&Eacute;PLACEMENT SILENCIEUX}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.ePLDf7VRIB41rsFE]{FRAPPER L&Acirc;CHEMENT}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-h.5qMuS8OawbKKGfbw]{TIRER CORRECTEMENT}</p>\n<p><strong>Comp&eacute;tences au choix :</strong></p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.UFGvKNWfbv15tees]{AMBIDEXTRIE}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.O7NcjuLet35LOSmH]{CHERCHER DES NOISES}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.2FdTwRRaWK5kZCpm]{CHEVAUCHER}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.xCDQtPg2uLpBsT9K]{&Eacute;RUDITION}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.bLzel3YuldOLHhQC]{ESCALADER}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.ezulXC71wGStV5fq]{M&Eacute;FIANCE}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.7hKKLXUqS3bKK1gY]{NAGER}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[naheulbeuk.competences-a.yBzkNeABxovvD9Qq]{RESSEMBLE &Ag