{"_id":"uTo05H49eaNWyyYi","name":"Bourgeois","type":"metier","img":"icons/svg/hanging-sign.svg","system":{"description":"<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>INT minimum : </strong>10, <strong>CHA minimum :</strong> 11</span></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Restrictions :</span></span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">➢</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">aucune restriction particuli&egrave;re, car le noble pense qu'il peut tout faire &ndash; ce qui est faux bien s&ucirc;r</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">➢</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"> </span><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">non, le noble ne peut choisir aucun autre m&eacute;tier que noble, m&ecirc;me &agrave; haut niveau !</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>EV initiale :</strong> selon origine</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-family: Naheulbeuk, Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Au niveau 1, le noble peut tirer une deuxi&egrave;me fois sa fortune et ajouter les pi&egrave;ces d'or &agrave; son p&eacute;cule de base. Il poss&egrave;de&nb